{"tid":1360301,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"出同唔出解放軍，有分別咩？","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:28:41.000Z","uid":268623,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb9cdfa2b17481c8878bc18978d26236a2f09fde","tid":1360301,"uid":268623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"「一國兩制」一早都已經盪然無存架啦，<br />\n<br />\n與其照以前咁溫水煮蛙煮到2047，<br />\n<br />\n不如提早將呢個美夢結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果今次輸左，接住黎一定係大搜捕、全面中國化，<br />\n<br />\n逼到你夠膽出解放軍，你中共就會無左香港呢條大水喉，大家一齊GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>if we burn you burn with us</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果唔夠膽出，贏既就係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS：如果香港人贏，成功爭取到自治，對你中國都有好處，大家齊齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4ea7e44905c0651f3782cf37b67c2cc51276d9","tid":1360301,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"橫掂2047都會一國一制<br />\n倒不如襯香港仲有影響力 人民仲有抵抗既勇氣 放手一搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3664984546ae35747acd9983c8d5486b64efb74e","tid":1360301,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"湊人數啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516e369e4a63c038aa69a81a1959b365995f28ad","tid":1360301,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9cdfa2b17481c8878bc18978d26236a2f09fde","tid":1360301,"uid":268623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"「一國兩制」一早都已經盪然無存架啦，<br />\n<br />\n與其照以前咁溫水煮蛙煮到2047，<br />\n<br />\n不如提早將呢個美夢結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果今次輸左，接住黎一定係大搜捕、全面中國化，<br />\n<br />\n逼到你夠